{"tid":1751121,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加或落手改革VAR","createTime":"2019-11-24T16:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:29:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c224f511325bb6738e128fad368d021da467e34c","tid":1751121,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】離開阿仙奴之後一直未有落班的雲加，最終都決定繼續在球壇工作，而他的首個任務將是完善VAR系統。<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》報道，日前雲加（Ars&egrave;ne Wenger）已經接受國際足協的邀請，成為新任的全球足球發展首長，而且身兼足球和技術諮詢小組委員。這個小組的工作，就是微調足球的比賽規例，研究並改善球場上的各種規則。當中最重要的一項工作，就是為今季為人咎病的英超VAR作出調整。<br />\n<br />\n英超前球證萊利（Mike Riley）認為雲加有足夠能力改善情況：「最惡劣的情況是，球證在場上作出了正確決定，但反而被VAR推翻了。這絕對可能發生。看看不同國家使用VAR，你就知道當中有一段學習的過程，這正是英格蘭正在經歷的事情。雲加的加盟是一個好機會，他可以影響更多人。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"f57964a942bf06f8c8b1a6029bf3d50cc628a7f2","tid":1751121,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/f6c8WJY6J58is/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Ff6c8WJY6J58is%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2b5c5e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThis man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9efeaf14fe03ed13e1a1439a05ede15967b79b","tid":1751121,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:06:50.000Z","msg":"炒左甸恩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n逼害左阿仙奴十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0613b252c5d8ca47d5f11e375ecd63b31f8da895","tid":1751121,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"黎緊哥帥高普摩狗so狗愛狗全部都要聽雲加支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}